OL,4,G0600FNotre-Dame: The Renaissance
OL,5,     GOver five years following the
OL,6,     Gdevastating fire, France's
OL,7,     Grenowned Notre-Dame de Paris has
OL,8,     Gonce again opened its doors,
OL,9,     Gmarked by a glamorous concert to
OL,10,     Ghonour its restoration.
